reviews.review_text: The Lobster Show Gets Some Love Good to see H.S. reappear and to do so with a first-time matrix treatment of a fantastic show (also did onw for the Providence show from a couple of nights before).  Many thanks for the hard work that went into this.  Trying to make the old Garden sound good is a monumental task and this one is up to the task.
